## Source

US Census Bureau; American Community Survey, 2023 American Community Survey 5-Year Estimates, [Table B08141](https://data.census.gov/table/ACSDT5Y2023.B08141?q=b08141&g=050XX00US36105,36027,36071,36119,36087,36079,36111_040XX00US36), April 2025
