## Note

The American Community Survey asks respondents in the workforce how many minutes it usually takes them to get from home to work. The travel time refers to a one-way trip on a typical day. This includes time spent waiting for public transportation, picking up passengers in carpools, and time spent in other activities related to getting to work. Sullivan County and Ulster County do have the same data according to the Census.
